		"description": "<p>Choose a damage type from the following list: acid, cold, fire, lightning, or poison. When you take damage of that type, you store some of its power to unleash it back on your foes. When you hit with your next attack, you may channel that energy into your strike and add 1d4 of the chosen type to your damage. This increases to 2d4 at 5th level, 3d4 at 11th level, and 4d4 at 17th level. You may use this ability a number of times equal to your Constitution modifier per long rest.</p>",
